title: PPPP’s Nawabzada Burhan Chandio wins PS-17 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP), Nawabzada Burhan Chandio has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-17, Qambar Shahdadokot-IV by securing 43885 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Javed Hussain Khokhar of Grand Democratic Alliance, who bagged votes 21,658.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 36.07 %.
